headline: Prudential Hong Kong commits HK$20 million to relief efforts for Wang Fuk Court and impacted customers
summary: Prudential Hong Kong extends its heartfelt condolences to the residents and families affected by the fire incident at Wang Fuk Court in Tai Po. We remain committed to providing practical support during this difficult time.
